 {The position is quite messy. Black has an extra Queen but White is ready with a 'windmill' against Black's King. Can you spot the best continuation for Black?} 4. Qd2+ {It is essential to place the Queen on d2 and not on a3. The difference will be clear soon.4...Qa3+?seems to be a winning move as was Black's choice in the game. But after5.Kb1Bf5+GM Firouzja found the only saving resource -6.e4=that dragged the game on and ultimately White was able to hold.} 
